data.description: Welcome to 45 Cindy Circle. This one and half story home features an elegant mix of open space interiors with three well appointed spacious  bedrooms on the main floor and two bathrooms, a sun room, eat in kitchen-with recently updated appliances, dining room and a large family room. Extending to the back yard is a fenced in oasis with an inviting inground pool and jacuzzi; great for those summer hang outs and barbeques! The fourth bedroom with a half bath is located above the garage with a massive unfinished area, awaiting your expansion!  This home is a great compilation of suburban tranquility that is within reach of all necessities close by.   Make this Covington beauty your next home!  * Seller Prefers to use Lueder, Larkin& Hunter Conyers/Tucker office!
